---
/**
 * InspirationBlock â€” "Why we built this"
 * One prominent quote + short explanation
 */
import { GridPattern } from "@/components/backgrounds/GridPattern";
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-16 md:py-24">
    <!-- Grid pattern background -->
    <GridPattern
        client:visible
        width={50}
        height={50}
        className="stroke-neutral-300/40 dark:stroke-neutral-700/30 mask-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,white,transparent_75%)]"
        squares={[
            [1, 2],
            [3, 4],
            [5, 1],
            [7, 3],
            [2, 6],
            [8, 5],
        ]}
    />

    <!-- Subtle gradient overlay -->
    <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-transparent via-muted/20 to-transparent"
        aria-hidden="true"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="container relative mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
            <!-- Quote -->
            <figure class="mb-8">
                <blockquote>
                    <p
                        class="text-2xl font-semibold italic tracking-tight text-foreground md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl"
                    >
                        "Most courses teach tools. We teach engineering
                        thinking."
                    </p>
                </blockquote>
            </figure>

            <!-- Explanation paragraph -->
            <div class="space-y-4 text-muted-foreground">
                <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
                    DevOps is not a checklist of tools. It is an approach to
                    design, automate, and operate systems reliably and securely.
                    Cloud Challenges was created because engineers need practice
                    solving <em>incomplete</em> problems: ambiguous specs, cost constraints,
                    failure modes, and trade-offs.
                </p>
                <p class="text-base font-medium text-foreground md:text-lg">
                    We provide the problems. You craft the solutions.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
